Package org.wmn4j.notation.elements

Class Chord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wmn4j.notation.elements.Chord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Note>, Durational
    public final class Chord
extends java.lang.Object
implements Durational, java.lang.Iterable<Note>
    Class for chords. This class should be used for chords where the notes are all of same length. For polyphonic textures add voices to the Measure. This class is immutable.
    Author:
    Otso Bj√∂rklund
